Open Standard License — STRUPER Reference Implementation

STRUPER — Structural Resolution Beyond Procedural Realization

Shunyaya Structural Realization Model

Legal Status

This license is a permissive Open Standard license for the STRUPER reference implementation.

To the maximum extent permitted by applicable law, this license grants rights similar in spirit to permissive open-source licenses, while preserving truthful representation requirements for the STRUPER name and reference implementation.

If any provision is found unenforceable, the remaining provisions remain in effect.

Nature of Release

This is a minimal, self-contained reference implementation.

It is intended to demonstrate a structural realization model — not to represent a full orchestration platform, realization runtime, workflow system, or procedural realization framework.

Behavioral guarantees apply only within the scope of the reference model and its defined structural assumptions.

